==English==
===Etymology===
Via French, from Latin [[colossus]], from Greek [[κολοσσος]] (originally used by [[w:Herodotus|Herodotus]] in reference to statues in ancient Egyptian temples).
[[Category:Latin derivations]] [[Category:Greek derivations]]

